<div id="faq-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="header-container">
        <h2 class="inverted rt-header">FAQ</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Who pays the finder’s fee?</h3>
        <p>
          The tutor whom ReferTutor contacted pays a finder fee prior to starting his/her job with the client you refer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>How much is finder’s fee?</h3>
        <p>
          Depending on the demand for a client, ReferTutor negotiates a reasonable finder fee with the tutors. Let us do the hard work and you can relax after refering a client to us!
        </p>
      </div>     
    </div> 
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>How long before I receive my finder’s fee?</h3>
        <p>
          Normally it takes a few weeks before a tutor accepts a job and start with the client you refer. If you don't hear from us after 30 days, please do not hesitate to contact us.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Who are the trusted tutors?</h3>
        <p>
          Tutors who join us have a detailed profile and we verify that information by phone discussion. Tutors are then asked to invite and connect with at least 3 other tutors. The more tutor connections a tutor has, the more he/she can be trusted.
        </p>
      </div>     
    </div> 
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>How are the tutors picked?</h3>
        <p>
          We only contact tutors who match your and their criteria. This way we avoid spamming our tutors with unsuitable jobs endlessly.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>I’ve more questions, how can I contact you?</h3>
        <p>
          The best way to reach us right now is by email: <a href="mailto:wongwf82@gmail.com">wongwf82@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>     
    </div> 
    <div class="row ta-center" style="margin-top: 50px;">
      <a href="#start-block" class="btn go">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

